<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Perfectism | Roblox World Hub</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="pill pill--brand">
      <span class="logo-mark" aria-hidden="true">⬤</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Perfectism</strong>
        <div class="pill__sub">Roblox universe</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="#sitemap">Sitemap</a>
      <a href="#highlights">Highlights</a>
      <a href="#portfolios">Team</a>
      <a class="pill pill--ghost" href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section id="hero" class="hero">
      <div class="hero__content">
        <p class="eyebrow">Roblox experience · Perfectism</p>
        <h1>Containment, strategy, and<br/><span class="gradient">a world built to be perfect.</span></h1>
        <p class="lede">Map every wing of Perfectism, point players to the right routes, and surface the portfolios behind the universe. Drop this page into your Roblox hub or community server for instant onboarding.</p>
        <div class="hero__actions">
          <a class="button button--primary" href="#sitemap">View sitemap</a>
          <a class="button button--ghost" href="#contact">Join Discord</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero__card">
        <div class="pill pill--inline">
          <span class="pill__title">Live world</span>
          <span class="pill__meta">Routes, staff contacts, and featured servers</span>
          <span class="pill__tag">Teleport map</span>
          <span class="pill__tag">Jobs</span>
          <span class="pill__tag">Events</span>
        </div>
        <div class="community-card" id="community">
          <div class="community__header">
            <p class="muted">COMMUNITY HUB</p>
            <span class="status status--green">Live now</span>
          </div>
          <div class="community__body">
            <div>
              <div class="muted">Roblox</div>
              <strong>Perfectism</strong>
              <p class="muted">A containment-driven RPG with rotating emergencies, side jobs, and lore hunts across the facility.</p>
            </div>
            <a class="button button--primary" href="#contact">Join Discord</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="sitemap" class="panel">
      <div class="panel__header">
        <p class="eyebrow">SITEMAP</p>
        <h2>Portal map for every wing</h2>
        <p class="lede">Swap in your own teleports and codes. These cards mirror the live routes players ask about most often.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid--3">
        <article class="card card--frost">
          <div class="card__badge">Start · Orientation</div>
          <h3>Central Atrium</h3>
          <p>Spawn deck with briefing kiosks, job board, and lifts that branch to every core route.</p>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Teleports: Labs · Operations · City</li>
            <li>NPC guide + tutorial tasks</li>
            <li>Daily missions & streak tracker</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card__badge">Routes</div>
          <h3>Operations Wing</h3>
          <p>Story arcs covering containment breaches, tech recovery, and timed evacuations.</p>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Chapter 1–5: Breach response</li>
            <li>Side jobs: Security · Research · Courier</li>
            <li>Fast travel unlocks per milestone</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="card card--outline">
          <div class="card__badge">Modes</div>
          <h3>Hazard Labs</h3>
          <p>Raids, breach events, stealth runs, and PvP simulations with rotating modifiers.</p>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Raids: 4–8 players, weekly bosses</li>
            <li>Breach: Timed containment events</li>
            <li>Sim Arena: Ranked & casual queues</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card__badge">Social</div>
          <h3>City Outskirts</h3>
          <p>Safe zone for trading, cosmetics, and world quests that send you back into the facility.</p>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Limited drops & featured gear</li>
            <li>Crafting recipes & blueprints</li>
            <li>Trust checklist for trades</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="card card--frost">
          <div class="card__badge">Lore</div>
          <h3>Archives</h3>
          <p>Audio logs, research trails, and puzzle doors that unlock new POIs.</p>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Collectibles & codex entries</li>
            <li>Puzzle doors with team keys</li>
            <li>Hidden portals for events</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card__badge">Support</div>
          <h3>Rules & Safety</h3>
          <p>Community standards, appeals, and moderator contacts.</p>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Code of conduct</li>
            <li>Report + appeal flow</li>
            <li>Support & incident desk</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="highlights" class="panel panel--alt">
      <div class="panel__header">
        <p class="eyebrow">HIGHLIGHTS</p>
        <h2>What keeps Perfectism players coming back</h2>
        <p class="lede">Quick hits you can update per season—swap the copy, leave the layout.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid--3">
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card__badge">Systems</div>
          <h3>Jobs with progression</h3>
          <p>Security, research, courier, and medics each with their own unlock ladders, payouts, and cosmetic perks.</p>
          <div class="chips"><span class="chip">Matchmaking</span><span class="chip">Streaks</span><span class="chip">Skill trees</span></div>
        </article>
        <article class="card card--frost">
          <div class="card__badge">Events</div>
          <h3>Rotating crises</h3>
          <p>Containment alerts, rogue AI protocols, and boss rotations with leaderboard rewards and exclusive drops.</p>
          <div class="chips"><span class="chip">Breach</span><span class="chip">Raid</span><span class="chip">Time trials</span></div>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card__badge">Community</div>
          <h3>Squads & socials</h3>
          <p>Form squads, share teleport codes, and plug your own studios or commissions without leaving the page.</p>
          <div class="chips"><span class="chip">Discord</span><span class="chip">Group links</span><span class="chip">Staff inbox</span></div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="portfolios" class="panel panel--alt">
      <div class="panel__header">
        <p class="eyebrow">TEAM</p>
        <h2>Builders, scripters, and artists behind Perfectism</h2>
        <p class="lede">Swap names, roles, and links. The layout keeps things consistent for commissions or recruitment.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid--3">
        <article class="profile">
          <div class="profile__avatar" aria-hidden="true">JR</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Jordan Reyes</h3>
            <p class="muted">Lead Builder · Environment design</p>
            <p>Stylized low-poly wings, cinematic lighting, and optimized maps for smooth play.</p>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">Roblox Studio</span><span class="tag">Lighting</span><span class="tag">Optimization</span>
            </div>
            <a class="button button--ghost" href="#">View portfolio</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="profile profile--accent">
          <div class="profile__avatar" aria-hidden="true">AK</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Alex Kim</h3>
            <p class="muted">Scripter · Systems & UI</p>
            <p>Lua systems for matchmaking, economies, and responsive UI across teleports.</p>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">Lua</span><span class="tag">UI/UX</span><span class="tag">Datastores</span>
            </div>
            <a class="button button--ghost" href="#">View portfolio</a>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="profile">
          <div class="profile__avatar" aria-hidden="true">SP</div>
          <div>
            <h3>Sasha Patel</h3>
            <p class="muted">VFX · Motion</p>
            <p>Performant particle systems, containment VFX, and cinematic trailers for updates.</p>
            <div class="tags">
              <span class="tag">VFX</span><span class="tag">Animation</span><span class="tag">After Effects</span>
            </div>
            <a class="button button--ghost" href="#">View portfolio</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="panel">
      <div class="panel__header">
        <p class="eyebrow">CONNECT</p>
        <h2>Stay in sync with the studio</h2>
        <p class="lede">Add your Discord, socials, or support link so players and collaborators can reach you quickly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="contact">
        <div class="card card--outline">
          <h3>Quick links</h3>
          <ul class="list list--inline">
            <li><a href="#">Discord</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Twitter</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">YouTube</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Support</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card card--frost">
          <h3>Newsletter</h3>
          <form class="form">
            <label for="email">Get update pings and devlogs</label>
            <div class="input-group">
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required />
              <button type="submit" class="button button--primary">Subscribe</button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <p>Perfectism · Roblox world hub</p>
    <p class="muted">Swap in your own teleport codes, quest IDs, and team links to make this your hub.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
